  "texts": [
    "266 H &E slides with grade 2-4 gliomas were gathered for their dataset from the TCGA and a private hospital.",
    "They presented a model based on using Resnet50 DCNN architecture as the primary structural support for IDH status prediction and generative adversarial networks (GAN) to produce synthetic samples to enable data augmentation.",
    "They also inferred that the DCNN model could predict IDH status more precisely when patients' ages are added as a new feature.",
    "They could identify the IDH mutational status with an accuracy of 85%.",
    "With accuracy rates of 83.25% and 82.1%, respectively, Bayramoglu et al."
  ],
